  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1576350/extras/c1d67263f324642c068e3b2d69d2ae2a.poster.avif?t=1646423701\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1576350/extras/c1d67263f324642c068e3b2d69d2ae2a.webm?t=1646423701\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1576350/extras/c1d67263f324642c068e3b2d69d2ae2a.mp4?t=1646423701\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Blair Witch: VR Edition is a story-driven psychological horror game based on the cinematic lore of Blair Witch. As Ellis, a former police officer with a troubled past, join the search for a missing boy in the iconic Black Hills Forest near Burkittsville, Maryland.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1576350/extras/81718f52f1dfda10e5c32410d75d1f20.poster.avif?t=1646423701\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1576350/extras/81718f52f1dfda10e5c32410d75d1f20.webm?t=1646423701\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1576350/extras/81718f52f1dfda10e5c32410d75d1f20.mp4?t=1646423701\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>What starts as an ordinary investigation soon will make you confront your darkest nightmares - and an ominous force known as the Blair Witch. But you’re not going in alone: your trusty K-9 sidekick, Bullet, is by your side. He’s your eyes, ears, and nose in these treacherous and terrifying woods.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1576350/extras/83f0298a9b5587836002a94f7e2a257b.poster.avif?t=1646423701\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1576350/extras/83f0298a9b5587836002a94f7e2a257b.webm?t=1646423701\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1576350/extras/83f0298a9b5587836002a94f7e2a257b.mp4?t=1646423701\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>The game has been rebuilt for VR to offer a uniquely immersive and horrifying VR experience. With environments redesigned for more interactivity, new Bullet mechanics - such as gesture commands, actual hand-based petting and fetching - and additional creature encounters, you will experience the eerie atmosphere of the Black Hills Forest like never before.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1576350/extras/33fc9207b1d667b48f48db70614ac4a9.poster.avif?t=1646423701\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1576350/extras/33fc9207b1d667b48f48db70614ac4a9.webm?t=1646423701\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1576350/extras/33fc9207b1d667b48f48db70614ac4a9.mp4?t=1646423701\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>These cursed woods will awaken your darkest fears.",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1576350/extras/c1d67263f324642c068e3b2d69d2ae2a.poster.avif?t=1646423701\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1576350/extras/c1d67263f324642c068e3b2d69d2ae2a.webm?t=1646423701\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1576350/extras/c1d67263f324642c068e3b2d69d2ae2a.mp4?t=1646423701\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Blair Witch: VR Edition is a story-driven psychological horror game based on the cinematic lore of Blair Witch. As Ellis, a former police officer with a troubled past, join the search for a missing boy in the iconic Black Hills Forest near Burkittsville, Maryland.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1576350/extras/81718f52f1dfda10e5c32410d75d1f20.poster.avif?t=1646423701\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1576350/extras/81718f52f1dfda10e5c32410d75d1f20.webm?t=1646423701\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1576350/extras/81718f52f1dfda10e5c32410d75d1f20.mp4?t=1646423701\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>What starts as an ordinary investigation soon will make you confront your darkest nightmares - and an ominous force known as the Blair Witch. But you’re not going in alone: your trusty K-9 sidekick, Bullet, is by your side. He’s your eyes, ears, and nose in these treacherous and terrifying woods.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1576350/extras/83f0298a9b5587836002a94f7e2a257b.poster.avif?t=1646423701\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1576350/extras/83f0298a9b5587836002a94f7e2a257b.webm?t=1646423701\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1576350/extras/83f0298a9b5587836002a94f7e2a257b.mp4?t=1646423701\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>The game has been rebuilt for VR to offer a uniquely immersive and horrifying VR experience. With environments redesigned for more interactivity, new Bullet mechanics - such as gesture commands, actual hand-based petting and fetching - and additional creature encounters, you will experience the eerie atmosphere of the Black Hills Forest like never before.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1576350/extras/33fc9207b1d667b48f48db70614ac4a9.poster.avif?t=1646423701\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1576350/extras/33fc9207b1d667b48f48db70614ac4a9.webm?t=1646423701\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1576350/extras/33fc9207b1d667b48f48db70614ac4a9.mp4?t=1646423701\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>These cursed woods will awaken your darkest fears.",
